Introduction

Daigo is a Japanese singer and trainee under SM Entertaiment. On June 17, 2022 he was revealed to be a new member of the boy group TO1 under WAKEONE.

Under his full name, Kobayashi Daigo, Daigo took part in the second season of Produce 101 Japan's "GyaO!" reality program in 2021. Regretfully, he was eliminated in the last episode, finishing in 13th place overall.

After Min Su, Jerome, and Woong Gi left TO1, it was revealed on June 17, 2022, that Daigo, Renta, and Yeojeong would be joining the group. The comeback was scheduled for July. On July 28, he made his debut with the group's third mini album, 'Why Not?'.
